"Predicons I know"lunarpine looking back and fourth between the two 
owls. "Who's the alliance?" "Who are you for that matter?"

Lunarpines senses tell him everyone's been scarred by this event. He 
understands, He can imagine the wilderness he was conditioned for 
suddenly being destroyed. 

"How'd you escape from looking like this?" (points to ship--- In 
nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Prowl::
> 
> Prowl looks from Lunarpine to Shadow Wing.
> 
> "The predacons attacked," he explains, "Shuko and his group were 
with them. 
> Then the Alliance came in, attacked them from behind, and left. We 
fought 
> back the rest of them, but the Ark's nearly destroyed."
